<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c1">"إنَّا آخذوها وشطر إبله عزمةٌ من عزمات ربِّنا"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وهذا كما قضى <span class="c1">"عمر"</span> -رحمه الله- على <span class="c1">"حاطب"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قال:</span> حدَّثنا <span class="c1">"عبَّاد بن عبَّاد"</span> عن <span class="c1">"محمَّد بن عمرو"</span> عن<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>